<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#006d98">قسورة:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(كَأَنَّهُمْ حُمُرٌ مُسْتَنْفِرَةٌ (٥٠)</span> فَرَّتْ مِنْ قَسْوَرَةٍ) <span style="color:#950000">" ٥١/المدثر "</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
